## Exercise

`convert()` function


::: {.cell}

```{.julia .cell-code}
days = 365
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.julia .cell-code}
days_float = convert(Float64, days) # Convert to Float64
#> 365.0
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.julia .cell-code}
days == days_float 
#> true
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.julia .cell-code}
@assert days == 365
@assert days_float == 365.0
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.julia .cell-code}
convert(Int64, "1") # Error
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.julia .cell-code}
parse(Int64, "1")
#> 1
```
:::
